Program to check whether the number is odd or even by using bitwise operator.
class number
{
public static void main(String args[])
     {
      int x=8;
      if((x&1)!=0)
  System.out.println("odd");
else
   System.out.println("even");
       }
}

output:
D:\tehari>javac oddeven.java
D:\tehari>java number
even
